data.description:
Escape to a 2412 sq ft wheelchair-accessible haven on 12.10 secluded acres. Designed with ease in mind, oversized doors, including pocket doors, ensure seamless movement. The garage, porch, and downstairs align on one level, adorned with 9ft ceilings. A 3/4 wrap porch provides picturesque views of ponds and a lush yard.

Say farewell to heating gas bills—the property boasts a drilled natural gas well with mineral rights. Revel in the natural beauty, with multiple ponds, including a new one at the front, surrounded by mature trees and vibrant dogwoods. Ideal as a home or event venue, the property is zoned residential.

This sanctuary features a loft, configured as a guest room, adding extra space. A short drive to Fayetteville, Devils Den State Park, and biking trails within 15 minutes. The sale includes appliances with an acceptable offer, making this retreat a turnkey escape. Immerse yourself in accessibility, natural beauty, and potential with this exceptional property
